{"tid":2151824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣作家顏擇雅：黎智英很有機會獲諾貝爾和平獎","createTime":"2020-08-11T15:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T01:51:33.000Z","uid":2054,"like":944,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"354b2f5e5a3e103bb2ff23216273594b7c1d8fd3","tid":2151824,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:01:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3256998\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3256998&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=38a8ea1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3256998&h=0332563c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3256998</a><br />\n2020-08-11 20:26:33<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕壹傳媒創辦人黎智英與數名高層昨（10日）遭香港警方以涉嫌違反《港版國安法》逮捕，消息震驚國際，包括《美聯社》、《路透》、《BBC》、《半島電視台》與《法新社》等國際重要新聞媒體，幾乎都以頭條新聞報導。對此，作家顏澤雅今天說，黎智英獲得諾貝爾和平獎的機會很大。<br />\n<br />\n顏擇雅在臉書表示，去年香港抗爭時，很多人說香港市民應該得諾貝爾和平獎，這點讓她存疑，「因為得獎人一向只有個人或組織，沒有城市人民的。何況，香港市民中許多人是『藍絲』（建制派支持者）」。<br />\n<br />\n顏擇雅說，但今天看到黎智英受到外媒的關注，尤其是照片中頂天立地的樣子，認為黎智英獲得諾貝爾和平獎的機會很大。「而且，從沒有報社老闆獲得這個獎。如果由他獲獎，對全世界新聞業會有很大啟示」。<br />\n<br />\n顏擇雅認為，黎智英的知名度夠大，相信歐美有許多政要會樂意幫忙寫推薦信，她也建議海外人權民主組織趕快分頭進行，去運作這件事。<br />\n<br />\n綜合港媒報導，黎智英昨被逮捕後，整夜被拘留在旺角警署，今（11日）早被押往西貢搜查其所擁有的遊艇，隨後回旺角警署，下午3點多再被押送至西九龍警察總部，至今仍未獲釋。"},{"pid":"589903e157dd3a5c68f6a1304a8925c4ab5aff1a","tid":2151824,"uid":314136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"d87d74c9e2c64db5c0068100e137a269299ca92e","tid":2151824,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591c1c64feda40bea8657e1908761798f5315a24","tid":2151824,"uid":13230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3182ccab4595356b9f0d24f73786ac8446ded4","tid":2151824,"uid":343361,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:05:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c68efc7d20a6eaa7847b3c1b5b969c3f52c9702","tid":2151824,"uid":13230,"like":257,"dislike":2,"score":255,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"佢俾拉個陣好型答左句: 煮到埋黎咪食囉"},{"pid":"7e90a0e1a3ab11908604ac340cd7a209e7bfd42e","tid":2151824,"uid":282435,"like":137,"dislike":1,"score":136,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:06:03.000Z","msg":"可否比晒所有無名抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n黎生代領"},{"pid":"4d47e49b3f78d6230ccd357d9d13cc56702e49cb","tid":2151824,"uid":70487,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"Jimmy對現屆美國政府有非常大影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"right\"><span class=\"medium\"><strong>[⇩ 美港形勢，唯一阻撓⇩]</strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"small\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pAcortX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pAcortX</a></span></p>"},{"pid":"4d29b9e54600b2ba6534d1016f485ea5e7392ad5","tid":2151824,"uid":243380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c68efc7d20a6eaa7847b3c1b5b969c3f52c9702","tid":2151824,"uid":13230,"like":257,"dislike":2,"score":255,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"佢俾拉個陣好型答左句: 煮到埋黎咪食囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4549dfdf60c838c4417acad254c0053fd3e1d1c","tid":2151824,"uid":30615,"like":84,"dislike":0,"score":84,"quote":{"pid":"7e90a0e1a3ab11908604ac340cd7a209e7bfd42e","tid":2151824,"uid":282435,"like":137,"dislike":1,"score":136,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:06:03.000Z","msg":"可否比晒所有無名抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n黎生代領"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"就算真係頒俾佢，都可能係空櫈2.0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e